  "text": "Specific to nursing, our results are consistent with research that found that personal attributes of persistence, self-directedness, empathy and altruism were vital attributes sought for in successful nurses [CITATION_1] ). Our findings also illustrate an Iranian symbol for a nurse -'Ms. Zeinab', a figure with admirable characteristics, including benevolence, kindness, honesty and self-confidence.",
